  "instructions": [
    "Mix soy sauce, cooking oil, garlic, lemon zest, rice vinegar, and brown sugar in a large bowl.",
    "Add shredded beef to the mixture and mix thoroughly. Marinate for at least 2 hours.",
    "Heat Kazan cauldron over medium-high heat.",
    "Pour marinated beef into the hot Kazan cauldron and cook for about 10 minutes, or until meat is charred and crumbly.",
